# PBTune-experiments repository
#
# This directory is tracked by a SEPARATE git repository
# (PBTune-experiments) and is gitignored by the parent PBTune repo.
#
# Workflow:
#   After experiments, commit and push from results/.
#   On local machine, clone PBTune-experiments into PBTune/results/.

# Ignore intermediate generation snapshots (bulky, reconstructable)
**/intermediate_generations/

# Ignore SMAC internal output (BO surrogate state)
**/smac_output/

# Ignore OS / editor junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*~
*.swp
